# The `SelectionDAGISel` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/selectiondagisel">SelectionDAGISel</a> - This is the common base class used for SelectionDAG-based pattern-matching instruction selectors. <a href="#details">More...</a>
